snippet.title: Above - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Website: http://play-above.com/
Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/743500/Above/
Discord: https://discord.gg/rBHtsqu

In Above you play as a heroic young pilot on a perilous journey across a vast flooded world, where lives revolve around the ancient evil beneath the waves. This aerial action adventure game takes you from humble beginnings in a fishing village to daring capers with sky pirates, sea monsters, murderous cultists and a cosmic scale mystery all in the quest to find your brother and uncover the truth behind his disappearance. 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/play_above
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playabove
